msgstr "nijigenerate 崩溃日志"

#: source/nijigenerate/utils/crashdump.d:85
#, c-format, d-format
msgid ""
"The application has unexpectedly crashed.\n"
"\n"
"If autosave is enabled, open File → Recent → Autosaves to recover your "
"work.\n"
"\n"
"A crash report was written to:\n"
"%s\n"
"\n"
"Please attach it when filing an issue:\n"
"https://github.com/nijigenerate/nijigenerate/issues"
msgstr ""
"应用程序意外崩溃。\n"
"\n"
"如果已启用自动保存，请打开“文件 → 最近 → 自动保存”来恢复工作。\n"
"\n"
"崩溃报告已写入：\n"
"%s\n"
"\n"
"提交 issue 时请附上该报告：\n"
"https://github.com/nijigenerate/nijigenerate/issues"

#: source/nijigenerate/utils/crashdump.d:282
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"===   nijigenerate has crashed   ===\n"
"Please send us the nijigenerate-crashdump.txt file in ~/Library/Logs\n"
"Attach the file as a git issue @ https://github.com/nijigenerate/"
"nijigenerate/issues"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"===   nijigenerate 已崩溃   ===\n"
"请发送 ~/Library/Logs 中的 nijigenerate-crashdump.txt 文件。\n"
"请在 GitHub issue 中附上该文件：\n"
"https://github.com/nijigenerate/nijigenerate/issues"

#: source/nijigenerate/utils/crashdump.d:287
msgid ""
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"===   nijigenerate has crashed   ===\n"
"Please send us the nijigenerate-crashdump.txt file in your log directory, "
"XDG_STATE_HOME. For Flatpak, this is in ~/.var/app/"
"nijigenerate.nijigenerate.\n"
"Attach the file as a git issue @ https://github.com/nijigenerate/"
"nijigenerate/issues"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"===   nijigenerate 已崩溃   ===\n"
"请发送日志目录 XDG_STATE_HOME 中的 nijigenerate-crashdump.txt 文件。Flatpak "
"版本的位置为 ~/.var/app/nijigenerate.nijigenerate。\n"
"请在 GitHub issue 中附上该文件：\n"
"https://github.com/nijigenerate/nijigenerate/issues"

#: source/nijigenerate/utils/crashdump.d:291
msgid ""
"The application has unexpectedly crashed\n"
"Please send the developers the nijigenerate-crashdump.txt which has been put "
"on your desktop\n"
"Via https://github.com/nijigenerate/nijigenerate/issues"
msgstr ""
"应用程序意外崩溃。\n"
"请通过 https://github.com/nijigenerate/nijigenerate/issues 将桌面上的 "
"nijigenerate-crashdump.txt 发送给开发者。"

